headline: Heavily Exposed to China, Casino Stocks Jump on Trade Deal
summary: Shares of casino operators Wynn Resorts, Las Vegas Sands, and MGM Resorts International surged to outpace the broader market Monday on news the U.S. and China agreed to slash tariffs for 90 days.
